Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡……就是你們這趟旅程的終點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問……妳到底是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:21.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終點?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.10,0:00:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是……
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到我的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…還有克勞德…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你們兩個能夠走到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了對你們的勇氣和努力表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就陪你們玩一玩好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在什麼地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
